Amanda Taylor, 24, has been charged with first-degree murder after she allegedly stabbed her former relative Charles Taylor, 59, in retaliation for her husband's suicide last year .
Taylor's suspected partner in crime, 32-year-old Sean Ball, was found wounded on the Blue Ridge Parkway in North Carolina .
The mother-of-two reportedly blamed her father-in-law for introducing her husband to drugs at a young age and driving him to suicide .